Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The World Duel Carnival has finally started!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Duel Champion will be named here in Heartland City among Duelists from all around the world in a fierce battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And naturally, that winner's gonna be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here goes! I'm gonna bring it-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! This ball has chosen you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck's with that ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ball's perplexity allows for good quality lifts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's always able to think up strategies for my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ball of cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me with the Heart Piece on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yuma Tsukumo, and you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kakeru Kunitachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru Kunitachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:00:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have I heard about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's kick-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrght! I'll bring it to em'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR vision - link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N-Duel!!\N-Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a Monster in Reverse Defense Mode and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've set Gogogo Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting you to Summon a Monster in Attack Mode on first impulse and battle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without stopping to properly gauge your enemy's deck and battle tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've improved a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop lecturing and watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got no clue as to who you're referring to, but I'll be shutting you up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the strength of my Soccer Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Field Magic, Dream Pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cat, I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We suddenly became commentators for a soccer match!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, this is the effect of the Field Magic, Dream Pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Field Magic, Dream Pitch can switch a face-down Defense Monster to face-up Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Summon Captain Wing from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1100 Attack Points?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An attack like that won't affect Gogogo Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Killer Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Captain Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for this turn, If Captain Wing fights a Monster with higher Defense Points than his Attack Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Attack Points are doubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's doubled or tripled, Gogogo Golem has an effect that prevents it from being destroyed once per turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Killer Pass, The battled Monster's Monster Effect is negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Captain Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra Bullet Shoot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? Even if you beat my Defense Mode Monster, my Life Points shouldn't have been damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Wing has an effect that deals damage to the opponent when its Attack Power is higher than the opponent's Defense Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...! This guy might be really strong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I get closer, I stretch my hand out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}towards that shining light leading towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dream of a world that expands from my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't a clue of where things like dreams and hopes are at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I run looking for it, I still can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I have fallen into a gap of truth and lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, our grand tale has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's move on towards tomorrow, \Neven if our road begins to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will jump forward, before all my\N strength completely drains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The closer I get, the further it becomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that truth that I must seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's to find hope that we desire from a future unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a heart stronger than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll learn to keep running up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the strength to win any battle, \Ndespite just how weak I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My purpose is to find,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with these invaluable friends of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of the world expanding\N from my feet with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel has just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(403,499)}"Numbers 27: WDC Kick-Off!\N Fire Striker Kakeru"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Bring it to em'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Gagaga Magician! Attack Captain Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good! Gagaga Magician's Attack Power is 1500!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Wing's Attack Power returned back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goooaaaal!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This goal is canceled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meo-why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I activated the Trap Card, Offside Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An offside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a Monster on my field is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this card negates the Monster's destruction and all Battle Damage, and the turn is forced to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Forced to end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observation #15...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In Soccer, your turn ends very abruptly."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is no time for your observations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, it's about time I got serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Striker Top!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He Summoned a Level Five Monster without release?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Field Magic Dream Pitch is activated, I can Summon Striker Top without release!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Striker Top!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now your goal is wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit him, Captain Wing! Direct attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Eye Contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With it's effect, I can return one Offside Trap from the Graveyard to my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he uses Offside Trap again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My attack will be negated again and my turn will be forced to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why're you napping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember anything about soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're so unreliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, what the heck should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long you think, it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't find a blind spot in my Soccer Deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you aren't going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're from the Soccer Representative Team...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Giant Strikers"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuto and Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru Kunitachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, he's the younger brother of Kazuto and Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Their dream-like consistent team plays has earned them fame all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three sons of the Kunitachi family!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that famous soccer player?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about my older brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Team play"? What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us end up getting in each other's way while we try to play at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I chose Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duels are the best battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because when you're on the field, you're the only person you can trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become Duel Champion with my own strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong about that, Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling is also about team plays!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team plays?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, you aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're out there fighting alongside your friends, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Captain Wing and Striker Top...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Monsters are your friends, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always believe in the Monsters I fight alongside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and my Monsters are a single team!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A team... you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you remember something about soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did. And Yuma, you helped me think up a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to lose in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon Zubaba Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one Summoning it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Zubaba Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And use the Resurrection of the Dead Magic Card to Special Summon Gogogo Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gogogo Golem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a team play, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then activate the Magic Card, Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Gogogo Golem from the Graveyard in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon all the Monsters you want! \NYou'll never break through my Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he activates that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use Cross Attack, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate the Cross Attack Magic Card from your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Cross Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have at least two Monsters on your side of the field with the same Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can attack the opponent player directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He scored a goal on me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job! You scored your first goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Yuma managed to lower Kakeru's Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! He figured out Offside Trap can't be activated against direct attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Zubaba Buster damages the opponent during an attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can destroy a Monster on the field with higher Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When using this effect, Zubaba Buster's Attack Power falls 500 points...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's well worth it to destroy a Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate the Quick-Play Magic, Runaway Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster is destroyed by an effect, the opponent is dealt 500 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally made it a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He caught up to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did ya see? That was my team playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not get cocky now, Yuma Tsukumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Wing was nothing more than a throw-away Monster with 1500 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying that worthless card gains you nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still saying stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to believe in your Monsters, your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless guys like them aren't my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God are you useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just pass the ball to me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... I'll do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kakeru, pass to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could trust any of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll settle this myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Kazuto and Hide's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a difference compared to his brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I heard he hurt his leg or something. I bet he just sucked from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You okay, Kakeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We lost because of you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God! You're all worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the worthless one, Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soccer isn't a one man show!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you can't figure that out, get the hell off this field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw away soccer on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I swore to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to settle things with my brothers one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've chosen Dueling to accomplish that goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the best in the world of Dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest with yourself, Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know it deep down, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have built such a strong Soccer Deck if you didn't, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your all-star team right there, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru, you really love soccer, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it! I don't care about soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Just like what you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So fight alongside your friends until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I.... you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Defender Libero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a Dream Pitch on my field, this Monster's level becomes five!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate the Magic Card, Team Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! You actually had a card like that from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have two Monsters on the field with the same level and type,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can Special Summon one Monster from your Graveyard with the same type.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring back Captain Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster Special Summoned with this effect increases its level by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's got three Level Five Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay the Level Five Striker Top, Defender Libero, and Captain Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network with these three Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, Fantasista Dieci!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got 2600 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, he won't make it out if he gets attacked by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Attack Zubaba Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, use your Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use Zubaba Buster as a target to activate the Trap Card, Half Unbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Zubaba Buster won't be destroyed because of this effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overhead Drive Shoot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Half Unbreak's effect halves the damage the player takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even at the cost of his own Life, for his Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You protected your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Fantasista's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detach an Overlay Unit so he can attack your Monster with the highest Attack Power again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gogogo Golem can't be destroyed in battle once per turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the second strike will end it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detach the final Overlay Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for the third attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zubaba Buster's the only one left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Fantasista!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overhead Drive Shoot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got the effect of Half Unbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You barely made it out of that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've only got 100 points left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ends in the next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry, Kotori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting against such a strong opponent is great! The Duel Carnival is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still think you can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have the Offside Trap on my side of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will win because I'll believe in my friends until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Gagaga Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1000 Attack Points?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why bother playing that Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's a Level Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon a new Xyz Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay the Level Three Zubaba Buster and the Level Three Gagaga Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network with these two Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, "Wandering Guitarist"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strummin' Fiend Itchy Rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate the Equipment Magic, Giant King!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip it to Itchy Rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card's effect prevents the opposing player from activating Magic and Traps until the End Phase of the turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Now I can't use Offside Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when the Monster equipped with Giant King attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if my Life Points are lower than my opponent's, the opponent's Monster has its Attack Power halved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Attack Power was halved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate the effect of Itchy Rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can detach one of its Overlay Units when it battles another Xyz Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to double its Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the match, Itchy Rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GOAL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Yuma made a complete turnaround in the very last moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:20:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Coz I had to borrow a bit of your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I got so consumed while playing soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soccer really is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Soccer" is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do love soccer the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who brought me back to my senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel that way, why don't you come back and give it another shot, Kakeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to our field!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you finally understand what we were trying to tell you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you told me back then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That soccer isn't a one man show?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I need to hurry and catch up to my brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna give soccer my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! I'm gonna give it my all to become Duel Champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I got my first piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win my next fight as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who the opponent is! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone gave me some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.55,0:22:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I was able to paint a rainbow with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to become someone perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with me suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't seem to grasp victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be having some kind of weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But If I must fulfill this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I don't mind being laughed at for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's because your limits are decided on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show it, overcoming it to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I'm aiming for the big blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For all of its glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Freesia of Desire.
